{"tid":1046774,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"琴行真係抽好多佣 :(","createTime":"2019-03-04T13:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:28:02.000Z","uid":98860,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c31f9000ac349a1949364635e3c87c5271f5e5a","tid":1046774,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"條女就幾年前考左鋼琴FTCL, 近日星期六會去琴行part time教琴。咁我之前就無問佢教琴收入既, 點知一問, 原來琴行抽50%佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 佢仲要教細路, 本來收350蚊45分鐘實收百幾蚊。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想幫佢搵啲7-8級/ AT/ LT 學生邊樹可以搵到。搵左幾個鐘多數學生都係初級, 可能高程度多數已經跟開一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n招喚連登音樂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ec57b125003b27853459319288c96f0ed170c7","tid":1046774,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4f30151739a34de81036e9e698587719d4da065","tid":1046774,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"有沒有人"},{"pid":"bf621d69df4c2dee1f0fd15e8151abba3bf8eb68","tid":1046774,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811d5fb3693ee05b00f39636aa90fb5d2ed14aba","tid":1046774,"uid":84830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"之前係荃灣做補習教chem，間補習社收人一堂（1.5hours) 450蚊，但佢就比我180蚊一堂only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果多過一個學生，我都係收180蚊，變相佢比愈多學生我，我就愈蝕，佢就賺到笑。"},{"pid":"51c115ffa9a0348bc516c4fe7b95252b8ec2c337","tid":1046774,"uid":160623,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"其實大部分都係抽50%, 我自己有studio揾老師教都係抽50%。"},{"pid":"f457195ac16a75cadb2e84c0091f7081e6b17477","tid":1046774,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike"